feature 
	V8 JavaScript Engine - compile javascript code to machine code to faster execution
	asyncronous and event driven
	Non-blocking I/O achive throungh Event Loop
	Single Threaded but Highly Scalable 
	Node.js library uses JavaScript
	Active and vibrant community
	No Buffering - depend on fs.readFile and fs.createReadStream

how works
	works asynchronously by using the event loop and callback functions
	Event Loop is a functionality which handles and processes all your external events and just converts them to a callback function.
	It invokes all the event handlers at a proper time
	
